			<center><h2 class="sum">About Us</h2></center>
			<p>This website was created by four girls: Raven Sims, Abigail Barnett, Michelle Bautista, and Laisha Calalpa. We are rising juniors in high school We are all part of the Girls Who Code Summmer Immersion Program. It is a 7-week coding program who's objective is to get more women to obtain a job in the computer science field. At the last two weeks of the program, we were required to create a website/app based on a topic we feel strong about. We came up with this website who's sole purpose is too provide educational opportunities and assistance to young undocumented immigrants. Many of them live with the stigma that your legal status determines the path of your education.</p>
